  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to collect simultaneous surface electrocardiogram (ECG)
      recordings and Cardiac Resynchronization Therapy (CRT) intracardiac electrogram (IEGM)
      recordings of variations in electrical synchrony.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
